# ── Large generated network files ───────────────────────────────────
# City networks are auto-generated; don't version large binary blobs.
# Exception: the bundled Sioux Falls example is pre-built and committed
# so collaborators can run `python runner.py` immediately after install.
*.osm
*.net.xml
*.rou.xml
*.sumocfg
!sioux_falls_network/*.net.xml
!sioux_falls_network/*.rou.xml
!sioux_falls_network/*.sumocfg

